           fniTransitionType 을 사용하여 특정 타입의 값을 from에서 to까지 정해진 시간동안에 변화시키는 작업을 위한 유틸리티 클래스


사용예시:

private static IEnumerator MoveRoutine(GameObject target, Vector3 from, Vector3 to, float duration, fniTransitionType progressType)

{

	target.transform.position = from;

	Vector3 curPos = from;

	fniProgression progress = new fniProgression(from, to, duration, progressType);

	while (progress.IsArrived == false)

	{

		yield return new WaitForEndOfFrame();

		progress.ProgressNextFrame(ref curPos);

		target.transform.position = curPos;

	}

	target.transform.position = to;

}

            오브젝트 회전 애니메이션(오일러각)

사용 방법

private void Do()

{

	StartCoroutine(Rotate("object"));

}



IEnumerator Rotate(GameObject target)

{

	yield return target.RotateTo(new Vector3(0, -90, 0), 1.0f, null, fniTransitionType.Linear));

	yield return target.RotateTo(new Vector3(0, -180, 0), 1.0f, null, fniTransitionType.Linear));

}

            오브젝트 회전 애니메이션(오일러각)

사용 방법

privte void Do()

{

	StartCoroutine(Rotate("object"));

}



IEnuerator Rotate(GameObject target)

{

	yield return target.RotateTo(target.transform.eulerAngles, new Vector3(0, -90, 0), 1.0f, null, fniTransitionType.Linear));

	yield return target.RotateTo(target.transform.eulerAngles, new Vector3(0, -180, 0), 1.0f, null, fniTransitionType.Linear));

}}

